  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>This is a minor release with\u00a0a few bug fixes.</p><h3 id=\"id-1.8.2-InventorySummaryExcel\">Inventory Summary Excel</h3><p>This was pointed at the wrong excel\u00a0template\u00a0(Inventory Item Details Excel), and is\u00a0now corrected.</p><h3 id=\"id-1.8.2-RemovingTicketItemsfromaReturnRepairTicket\">Removing Ticket Items from a Return Repair\u00a0Ticket</h3><p>Ticket items could not be removed from a return repair ticket due to an error. This is now fixed.</p><h3 id=\"id-1.8.2-BatchInvoicePrint\">Batch Invoice Print</h3><p>The print template for batch invoices was not loading due to an error. This has been fixed.</p><h3 id=\"id-1.8.2-AccountManagement\">Account Management</h3><p>The\u00a0minimum users and locations required when updating your RepairQ license was not including the user and location that come with the base license. This has been resolved (effectively reducing the minimum for each by 1)\u00a0</p>",
      "representation": "export_view",
